ssr.nameservice

クラス CorbaNamingManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • ssr.nameservice.CorbaNamingManager

  • public class CorbaNamingManager
extends java.lang.Object
    CorbaNaming object Manager. get method provides CorbaNaming access by using URI. The binded CorbaNaming object will be automatically stored in this class's static object. The next call will be much faster.
    作成者:
    ysuga
